	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. (names entire); Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; Zon. 8.19; Degrassi 44f., 117f., 440f. Both Consuls campaigned in Liguria (Zon. 8.19)." .
